title: Maureen O'Hara, spirited movie star, dies at 95
text:
> Entertainment Maureen O'Hara, spirited movie star, dies at 95 FILE - This Jan. 19, 1960 file photo shows movie actress Maureen O'Hara photographed in her front yard in Los Angeles. O'Hara,who appeared in such classic films as "The Quiet Man” and How Green Was My Valley," has died. Her manager says O’Hara died in her sleep Saturday, Oct. 24, 2015 at her home in Boise, Idaho. (AP Photo/Harold Filan,File)
